        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Protecting Patient Access to Lifesaving COVID-19 Drugs Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill requires health insurance plans to cover COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) antibody treatment at no cost for individuals who have tested positive for the virus.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
